==== Worldcat - Ruby port of the worldcat Python module ====

Worldcat intends to make use of OCLC's WorldCat Affiliate web services:
http://www.worldcat.org/affiliate/

*Important*
This version only supports the OCLC xID (xISSN, xISBN, xOCLCNUM) web services.

=== Installation

Edit the <plugin>/config/worldcat.yml file.  This file requires your:

* Affiliate ID
* WSKEY code (currently using Terry Reese's wcapi gem wskey key)

=== Usage?

Run the rake task: rake worldcat:test

Basics
>> script/console
>> x = XISBNRequest.new('1888363886', {:format => 'xml', :method => 'to13'})
>> x.valid?
>> y = x.get_response
>> y.evaluated?
>> y.data

See each XIDRequest subklass for format and method options.

